Class ToStringHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • functions.ToStringHelper

  • public class ToStringHelper
extends Object
    A mutable String representation of an arbitrary object.

    This class allows for the specification of a name during construction as well as chaining of the add(java.lang.String, java.lang.Object) operation.

    Author:
    Oliver Abdulrahim
